---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <div class="aboutus">
    <div class="aboutus-content">
      <h2>About FinEdge</h2>
      <p>
        FinEdge is a cutting-edge fintech startup revolutionizing cross-border
        payments. Our mission is to transform the way individuals and businesses
        make transactions, breaking down geographic boundaries and enabling
        seamless global financial connectivity.
      </p>
      <p>
        With our innovative technology and expertise, we empower individuals and
        businesses to overcome the challenges associated with cross-border
        payments. Our secure and reliable platform ensures fast, transparent,
        and cost-effective transactions, fostering financial inclusivity and
        driving global economic growth.
      </p>
      <p>
        At FinEdge, we believe that everyone should have access to efficient and
        affordable cross-border payment solutions. By leveraging the latest
        advancements in fintech, we are shaping a future where geographic
        limitations are no longer obstacles, and individuals and businesses can
        thrive in a borderless financial ecosystem.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you are an individual looking to send money to family and
        friends overseas or a business seeking streamlined payment solutions,
        FinEdge has you covered. Our dedicated team is committed to providing
        exceptional service and ensuring your financial transactions are handled
        with the utmost care and efficiency.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .aboutus {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #24c6dc, #514a9d);
    color: white;
    padding: 40px;
  }

  .aboutus-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .aboutus-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .aboutus-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* Responsive Styles */

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .aboutus-content {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
